header.gameNote: ROSE BOWL GAME PRESENTED BY NORTHWESTERN MUTUAL

videos.description: Justin Herbert calls his own number as he stiff-arms a defender and runs four yards for the Ducks' first touchdown of the day.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Herbert stiff-arms defender on way to TD) 2020/1/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Herbert stiff-arms defender on way to TD

videos.description: Wisconsin's Aron Cruickshank responds to Oregon's opening-drive touchdown with a 95-yard kickoff return for a TD.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Wisconsin returns kickoff 95 yards for TD) 2020/1/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wisconsin returns kickoff 95 yards for TD

videos.description: Wisconsin's Jack Sanborn picks off Justin Herbert's pass into heavy traffic.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Badgers pick off Herbert's pass) 2020/1/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Badgers pick off Herbert's pass

videos.description: Jonathan Taylor has the ball ripped away from him during a run and Oregon recovers.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Taylor fumbles ball, Oregon recovers) 2020/1/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Taylor fumbles ball, Oregon recovers

videos.description: Jack Coan's pass is picked off by Oregon's Thomas Graham Jr. late in the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Coan's pass picked off by Ducks) 2020/1/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Coan's pass picked off by Ducks

videos.description: Justin Herbert bounces to the outside for a five-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Herbert goes untouched for Oregon TD) 2020/1/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Herbert goes untouched for Oregon TD

videos.description: Quintez Cephus makes a touchdown catch to grab the lead for the Badgers just before halftime.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Cephus hauls in TD just before halftime) 2020/1/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cephus hauls in TD just before halftime

videos.description: Oregon's Brady Breeze scoops up Anthony Lotti's fumbled punt and runs it all the way back for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Oregon scores on Wisconsin's botched punt) 2020/1/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oregon scores on Wisconsin's botched punt

videos.description: Wisconsin fakes the handoff to Jonathan Taylor and instead goes to Mason Stokke who plows in for the Badgers' touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Badgers fake to Taylor, score with Stokke) 2020/1/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Badgers fake to Taylor, score with Stokke

videos.description: Justin Herbert has his third rushing touchdown of the day due to another Brady Breeze turnover to grab the lead from Wisconsin.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Oregon fumble recovery turns into Herbert TD) 2020/1/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Oregon fumble recovery turns into Herbert TD

videos.description: Justin Herbert breaks off three rushing touchdowns vs. Wisconsin as Oregon wins the Rose Bowl 28-27.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Justin Herbert runs for 3 TDs in Rose Bowl win) 2019/1/1 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Justin Herbert runs for 3 TDs in Rose Bowl win
